flowchart LR
    SRC[Sender Service]

    SRC --> SELECT{transport selection}
    SELECT -->|primary| HTTPS[HTTPS / REST]
    SELECT -->|streaming| WS[WebSocket]
    SELECT -->|async| QUEUE[Message Queue]
    HTTPS --> GW[API Gateway]
    WS --> GW
    QUEUE --> GW

    GW --> OK{delivered?}
    OK -->|yes| DONE[success]
    OK -->|no: HTTPS timeout| FALLBACK[fallback to QUEUE]
    OK -->|no: WS disconnect| FALLBACK
    FALLBACK --> RETRY[retry with backoff]
    RETRY --> DONE
